<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.889171>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Female of Tineobius (Tineobius) tamaricis Ribes & Fusu sp. nov. A. Habitus of holotype before card mounting. B. Mesosoma (paratype 13940). C – G. Paratype 10077. C. Habitus. D. Antenna. E. Head. F. Fore wing. G. Head and mesosoma, dorsal view. H. Metanotum and propodeum (paratype 13940). Scale bars: A, C = 1 mm; B, D – H = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/889171/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

